Description.SourceString: Some levels require either Lockpicks or specific, named Treasure Maps to enter. Unlike other levels, it is not possible to receive a partial completion reward for exiting or failing Treasure Map levels. Treasure Maps and Lockpicks are only spent if the level is successfully completed, meaning you can replay failed levels without penalty. Super boss levels with Treasure Maps or Lockpicks can often be very long.
